# Create New Email Account

- Login to Plesk Panel as admin
- Go to **Domains** >> click on **Manage Hosting** link of the corresponding domain name you want to setup new e-mail account.
- In the new window click on **Mail** Tab and then click on **Create New E-mail Address**.

```diagram

```

- In the next window write your email address, select the mail box size and put your password.
- Then click on OK button to create new email address under your account.

## How to reset E-mail Account Password

Login to Plesk Panel as admin
Go to **Domains** >> click on **Manage Hosting** link of the corresponding domain name you want to setup new e-mail account.
In the new window click on **Mail** Tab and then click on the email account you want to reset password. 
In the new window put the new password in the Password text field and confirm it again. Then click on **OK** button


## How to setup Email Forwards / Auto-Reply / Email Alias / Anti Virus

- Login to Plesk Panel as admin
- Go to **Domains** >> click on **Manage Hosting** link of the corresponding domain name you want to setup new e-mail account.
- In the new window click on **Mail** Tab and then click on the email account you want to setup forwards/auto response/Email alias

**Setup Email Forwards**

Set up forwarding of e-mail messages to one or several e-mail addresses. If your mailbox is switched on under the General tab, then copies of e-mail messages will be kept in it.

- In the new window click on **Forwarding**.
- By default it is disabled. You have to select "**Switch on mail forwarding**" first.
- Then put your email address in the below text area and then click on **OK** button to setup forwarding. 

**Setup Auto-Reply**

Set up an automatic response to any mail message coming to your e-mail address. Auto-reply is a standard means to notify your correspondents that you are out of office or on vacation.

- Click on **Auto Reply** button.
- By default it is disabled. You have to select "**Switch on auto-reply**" first.
- Fill up the form correctly and then click on **OK** button to setup auto reply on your email address.
